item.description:
Caffe Caffe is a Deep Learning framework by Berkeley Vision and Learning Center(BVLC) and by community contributors. Yangqing Jia created the project during his PhD at UC Berkeley. Caffe is released under the BSD 2-Clause license.
Introduction Deep Learning &hellip;
I am a fresh man in Deep Learning filed, so maybe Caffe is a good start for the first lesson. I encountered so many issues when I was trying to install Caffe which cost me a lot of time to find the correct solutions.
